    dc:description "FIGURES 65 – 69. Figs. 65 – 67: Spadiseius spathiphyllae n. sp., adult male: 65, tarsus IV, dorsolateral view, without pretarsus; 66, 67, femora IV, dorsal view: 66, “ short-haired ” morph; 67, “ long-haired ” morph. Figs. 68, 69, Spadiseius calyptrogynae n. sp., adult male, femora IV, dorsal view: 68, “ wartless ” morph; 69, “ warted ” morph." ;
